{"tid":648761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：內地團激戰影相檔 武俠金紫荊　廿人群揪","createTime":"2018-05-01T03:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T04:56:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ece9ecdde9f01ff281fe6da49364ef7f9de37fe9","tid":648761,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:47:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180501/20378048?_ga=2.108645378.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20378048%3F_ga%3D2.108645378.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=uWXdQhWoVnubLJeAKiDwLr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e62a9801\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20378048%3F_ga%3D2.108645378.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=5e2216c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180501/20378048?_ga=2.108645378.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月01日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：內地團激戰影相檔<br />\n武俠金紫荊　廿人群揪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180501/large/a0903a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180501%2Flarge%2Fa0903a.gif&h=5f20cf8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■廿人大混戰，打打吓連導遊旗仔（紅圈示）都當武器。讀者阿明提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n灣仔金紫荊廣場係內地旅客指定打卡旅遊點，上個禮拜三就發生咗一宗內地旅客同影相檔職員嘅打交案，20幾人打埋一齊，又飛腳又直拳，仲有人搶埋導遊支旗仔當武器。呢場MMA最終不分勝負，因為警察嚟到分別拉咗內地旅客同影相檔職員各3人。有導遊就話金紫荊廣場影相檔亂七八糟，係時候要整頓吓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180501/large/a0903b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180501%2Flarge%2Fa0903b.gif&h=d1afc86d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■呢位阿哥撲前出拳，拳拳到肉。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180501/large/a0903c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180501%2Flarge%2Fa0903c.gif&h=1d05c8f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導遊旗仔當武器<br />\n<br />\n拍片嘅阿明本身係導遊，上周三中午佢帶團去金紫荊廣場，將一車車嘅大叔大媽車去金紫荊雕塑前影相，當時喺廣場嘅10檔影相檔職員就走出嚟推銷攝影套餐，「8吋大相15元人民幣」，十分墟冚。<br />\n<br />\n點知無耐就有影相檔職員同幾個內地旅客嘈交，講唔掂就打起上嚟，當時有20幾人圍埋一齊，大家拳來腳往，混亂中仲有人連鞋都甩埋，好鬼狼狽，連內地導遊嗰支旗仔都俾人搶埋當武器追住人嚟打，搞到呢個「神聖廣場」烏煙瘴氣。<br />\n<br />\n片段中最精采就係4、5個大叔大哥打埋身肉搏，其中一個着住黑白格仔衫嘅阿哥最衝動，一撲前就連出4拳，直拳、鈎拳，重拳，連環拳，有人中拳之後都退咗幾步，真係戥佢肉痛。因為趕住帶團，阿明之後上車走咗，唔知呢場金紫荊大戰最終誰勝誰負。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人話，上星期三中午12點44分喺金紫荊廣場發生一宗「公眾地方打交」案，分別拘捕3個內地男子同3名影相檔職員，事後其中兩個職員同一個內地遊客被落案，稍後將提堂審理。《蘋果》事後去番金紫荊廣場，發現嗰度有10個影相檔，但問番單打交事件，個個職員都異口同聲話「唔知，無聽過」。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：議員：影相檔無牌經營<br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：議員：影相檔無牌經營"},{"pid":"a31da82aed223c7e855410dbf6e576ac1441bc29","tid":648761,"uid":150935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 張圖畫出黎？"},{"pid":"8bc5cfdfb455a11178e49c134b98cccd84af598d","tid":648761,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"抵死啦<br />\n狗奴才<br />\n<br />\n敢逆主子意<br />\n打撚死你班影相佬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img01.haolishi.com/2017-05/21/01/1495301934350_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg01.haolishi.com%2F2017-05%2F21%2F01%2F1495301934350_0.jpg&h=7748d104&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31687b46ac4d078475ccce66a2ce33fe418c9a99","tid":648761,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"武俠金紫荊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cf14965ec3d3435f962cf487471a088263fe03","tid":648761,"uid":67346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"2018年仲係出唔到一張高清嘅圖"},{"pid":"859cb93295a119161d58131de10ae35037ddf80b","tid":648761,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗"},{"pid":"3a04a720e8faf6168f721b01eb65837bec40b605","tid":648761,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"幫手打撚爛埋個核突支那style金紫荊啦唔該"},{"pid":"e73e51686fb93d45da7e0889acede1c8d9db5457","tid":648761,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"沙灘都紮得營<br />\n唔爭在呢度"}]}